name: Scull
description: Aren't the skulls adorable? Do they not keep the secret of the creation? Skulls are never enough or there would be no secrets that are needed to unlock more evil mysteries. What makes the skull perfect in this case is that the addition of large skulls can give me insight into the horror-stories behind skulls. All through this 'game' the sounds from the shadows and sounds of the 'game' made my heart growrier and my ears heard a pain my ears were afraid to bear.
